FBIS3-48582 "dreas017_n_94008" FBIS-EAS-94-017 Document Type:Daily Report 26 Jan 1994 Vietnam Newspaper: KR Oredered To Kill Fisherman BK2601155894 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 2300 GMT 25 Jan 94 BK2601155894 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network Language: Vietnamese Article Type:BFN [Text] The newspaper CAMBODIA LIFE on 19 January quoted sources as saying that a Khmer Rouge [KR] general named Chhit Choeun or Mok, now on convalescence in the triborder area of Cambodia, Laos, and Thailand has ordered Khmer Rouge's 980th [as heard] Division headed by (Muol) to resume its intensified operations around the Tonle Sap lake area to kill fishermen of Vietnamese origin who are earning their living by fishing in the Tonle Sap lake.
